      "text": "receives and transforms logs,\nextracts fields, indexes them\nand forwards them to Opensearch\nVery fast and lightweight (Rust based)",
      "fontSize": 19.238089425223194,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "receives and transforms logs,\nextracts fields, indexes them\nand forwards them to Opensearch\nVery fast and lightweight (Rust based)",
