    {
      "id": "hziAr0ZWtw0dREisxr18S",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 164.52763296452247,
      "y": 1362.0744319171372,
      "width": 1029.5294189453125,
      "height": 110.64687465147819,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "#e03131",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cRbh",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1170496716,
      "version": 477,
      "versionNonce": 674427530,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768568188278,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The biggest problem here is to have the same event in the ingest and storer service and then they generate the same \nmessage id for the same event, otherwise we'll have duplicate processing.\nFirst idea to get generate the message id from combinating timestamp-pair-volume \n\n",
      "fontSize": 17.70349994423651,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The biggest problem here is to have the same event in the ingest and storer service and then they generate the same \nmessage id for the same event, otherwise we'll have duplicate processing.\nFirst idea to get generate the message id from combinating timestamp-pair-volume \n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wmRKSXyPsDo5Db4MHl4tm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1394.6319788243875,
      "y": -218.2585488986108,
      "width": 419,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cRbi",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2039258001,
      "version": 243,
      "versionNonce": 1586680598,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768568188278,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Read and Processor app can be made into \none app, but then the websocket will\ncompete with the kafka consumers \nfor the same resources.\nAlso with separate apps we can scale\nthem separately.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Read and Processor app can be made into \none app, but then the websocket will\ncompete with the kafka consumers \nfor the same resources.\nAlso with separate apps we can scale\nthem separately.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1szDakGJrb7JkMQpcYUeg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1908.6795688076468,
      "y": -497.449004744035,
      "width": 524.7647094726562,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cRbj",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 114386801,
      "version": 172,
      "versionNonce": 654840138,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768568188278,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The reason for the job filling the cache is so \nthat we don't block the reads from the websocket.\nThe job will only fetch pairs that have been updated.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The reason for the job filling the cache is so \nthat we don't block the reads from the websocket.\nThe job will only fetch pairs that have been updated.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p1a1ZlEoZ2XK-yn8D6D4J",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2151.48213317297,
      "y": 6437.768569478022,
      "width": 5176.7353515625,
      "height": 131.95999162486748,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cRbk",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 202851453,
      "version": 356,
      "versionNonce": 976486486,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768568188278,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CoinSight - Monolith 2, Sink DB to Kafka (Dropped, too slow couples processing and event storage)",
      "fontSize": 105.567993299894,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CoinSight - Monolith 2, Sink DB to Kafka (Dropped, too slow couples processing and event storage)",
