      "text": "historical data\nfor analytical purposes\nLong term storage with\ncolumnar compression\nThe compression reduces memory footprint \nand increases search query performance.\nData will be compressed after 10 mins of its \narrival.\n\nAlso used for event storage\n\nNeed to have at least 1 replica",
